    "body": "<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n\n## Purpose\nThe purpose of this PR is to add support for Full CUDA Graphs and Piecewise CUDA graphs to Mamba1 models.\n\nI had also moved some common logic for mamba models to a new base class due to shared code. @tdoublep Let me know what you think.\n\n## Test Plan\n- Tests in `test_hybrid.py` passed and added a new check for `test_full_cuda_graph` which checks Jamba.\n- Ran `lm_eval`\n- Ran `vllm benchmark latency`\n## Test Result\n\nLatency Results - \n```bash\n**V0 with FCG**\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=0  python benchmark_latency.py \\\n        --model ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8 \\\n        --input-len 31500 \\\n        --output-len 128 \\\n        --batch-size 1  \\\n        --num-iters-warmup 3 \\\n        --num-iters 3 \\\n        --max-num-seqs 1\n\nAvg latency: 5.413307532668114 seconds\n10% percentile latency: 5.40432041650638 seconds\n25% percentile latency: 5.406467076041736 seconds\n50% percentile latency: 5.4100448419339955 seconds\n75% percentile latency: 5.418516643927433 seconds\n90% percentile latency: 5.423599725123495 seconds\n99% percentile latency: 5.426649573841132 seconds\n**No CUDA GRAPH**\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=FLASHINFER python benchmark_latency.py \\\n        --model ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8 \\\n        --input-len 31500 \\\n        --output-len 128 \\\n        --batch-size 1  \\\n        --num-iters-warmup 3 \\\n        --num-iters 3 \\\n        --max-num-seqs 1 \\\n        --enforce-eager\nProfiling iterations: 100% 3/3 [00:14<00:00,  5.00s/it]\nAvg latency: 4.998069426355262 seconds\n10% percentile latency: 4.991475126799196 seconds\n25% percentile latency: 4.994978636037558 seconds\n50% percentile latency: 5.0008178181014955 seconds\n75% percentile latency: 5.002534412546083 seconds\n90% percentile latency: 5.003564369212836 seconds\n99% percentile latency: 5.004182343212888 seconds\n\n**Piecewise**\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=FLASHINFER python benchmark_latency.py\n         --model ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8\n         --input-len 31500\n         --output-len 128\n         --batch-size 1\n          --num-iters-warmup 3\n         --num-iters 3\n         --max-num-seqs 1 \n\nProfiling iterations: 100% 3/3 [00:12<00:00,  4.24s/it]\nAvg latency: 4.244465307487796 seconds\n10% percentile latency: 4.234823149256409 seconds\n25% percentile latency: 4.236879565520212 seconds\n50% percentile latency: 4.240306925959885 seconds\n75% percentile latency: 4.249971858691424 seconds\n90% percentile latency: 4.2557708183303475 seconds\n99% percentile latency: 4.259250194113702 seconds\n\n**FCG**\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=FLASHINFER python benchmark_latency.py\n         --model ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8\n         --input-len 31500\n         --output-len 128\n         --batch-size 1\n         --num-iters-warmup 3\n        --num-iters 3\n        --max-num-seqs 1\n        --compilation-config='{\"cudagraph_mode\": \"FULL\"}'\n\nAvg latency: 3.102836686031272 seconds\n10% percentile latency: 3.100900445878506 seconds\n25% percentile latency: 3.101404333487153 seconds\n50% percentile latency: 3.102244146168232 seconds\n75% percentile latency: 3.103972768643871 seconds\n90% percentile latency: 3.1050099421292545 seconds\n99% percentile latency: 3.1056322462204844 seconds\n```\n\n`lm_eval` Results:\n```bash\nNO CUDA (`enforce_eager=True`)\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=FLASHINFER lm_eval --model vllm --model_args pretrained=ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8,enable_prefix_caching=False,enforce_eager=True,max_num_seqs=64 --tasks gsm8k --num_fewshot 5 --batch_size auto --limit 500\n\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value|   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.304|±  |0.0206|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.248|±  |0.0193|\n\n\nPiecewise\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=FLASHINFER lm_eval --model vllm --model_args pretrained=ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8,enable_prefix_caching=False,enforce_eager=False,max_num_seqs=64 --tasks gsm8k --num_fewshot 5 --batch_size auto --limit 500\n\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value|   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.292|±  |0.0204|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.232|±  |0.0189|\n\n\nFCG (Modified `lm_eval` to support it)\n\nVLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=FLASHINFER lm_eval --model vllm --model_args pretrained=ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Mini-1.7-FP8,enable_prefix_caching=False,enforce_eager=False,max_num_seqs=64 --tasks gsm8k --num_fewshot 5 --batch_size auto --limit 500\n\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value|   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.292|±  |0.0204|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.230|±  |0.0188|\n```\n\n## (Optional) Documentation Update\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [x] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [x] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [x] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [x] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n</details>\n",
